text.section:
The subtraction under subsection (a) of this section includes the amounts allowed to be subtracted for an individual under:
§ 10-207(i) of this title (Profits on sale or exchange of State or local bonds);
§ 10-207(k) of this title (Relocation and assistance payments);
§ 10-207(m) of this title (State or local income tax refunds); or
§ 10-207(c-1) of this title (State tax-exempt interest from mutual funds).
